snippet.title: Amber Heard Says She's A Pro-Gun Advocate & Sleeps With A Firearm, As It Makes Her Feel Safe
snippet.description:
Yeah, I took my time with this intro.  I decided to let it breathe. So please feel free to skip the beginning and jump ahead to: 04:05. Or just skip the whole video entirely. Either way, I'm not mad at ya. 

If this is your 1st time to my channel, then you will realize (pretty quickly) that we do the news a little bit differently around here. 

First things first: I have a imaginary friends, like I have many of them in fact. I also have stuffed animals who I talk to regularly. (if you talk to your plants, you'll understand) And as a matter of fact one of them is my co-host. 
Also before you ask, I wear a mask because I'm Ugly AF and I don't want to get doxed because I'm not a group thinker or liberal/media shill. & yeah.. I wear a hello kitty back back, I love using lotion, the only pants I own are sweats, I live in my moms basement, I eat pizza rolls and hot pockets, I vape because its the only way to keep me off cigarettes and I personally identify as a non binary vegan unicorn..  SO please respect my proper pronouns - Unir/Unis/Uniye. 

Welcome to Darth News Mother Fudgers.
